            "text": "<p>This statement applies to the website: <a href=\"https://robertocoin.com/\"><strong>www.robertocoin.com</strong></a><br/>Last updated: 27/06/2025</p><p>Roberto Coin S.p.A. is committed to ensuring digital accessibility for all users, including persons with disabilities, in accordance with the <strong>European Accessibility Act</strong> <strong>(Directive (EU) 2019/882)</strong> and the applicable <strong>Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG)</strong>, version 2.1 (or later), level <strong>AA</strong>.</p><p>We are continuously working to improve the accessibility of our website and digital content, and we consider accessibility an ongoing and integral part of our digital strategy.</p><p>Please note that accessibility improvements may be rolled out progressively, and some areas of the website may reach compliance at different times.</p><p><strong>Contact us</strong></p><p>If you experience any difficulty accessing information on this website, or if you would like to request accessible alternatives for specific content, please contact us at:</p><p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:customercare@robertocoin.com\">customercare@robertocoin.com</a><br/>Phone: <a href=\"tel:+39 0444 202 216\">+39 0444 202 216</a></p><p>You can also write to us at:</p><p>Roberto Coin S.p.A.<br/>Viale Trieste 13<br/>Vicenza, 36100,<br/>Italy</p>",
